  "instructions": [
    "Heat 2 tablespoons of butter in a large Dutch oven over medium heat.",
    "Infuse genmaicha tea into the chicken broth, then strain and set aside.",
    "Add the onion to the pot and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the mushrooms and cook until they release their liquid and start browning, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the chicken and cook until browned on all sides, about 5-7 minutes.",
    "Add the white wine and cook until reduced by half, about 2-3 minutes.",
    "Add the flour and whisk to combine, cooking for 1 minute.",
    "Add the infused broth and bring to a simmer.",
    "Reduce heat to low and cook, covered, until the chicken is cooked through, about 15-20 minutes.",
    "Stir in the pickle, caraway seeds, and garlic.",
    "Transfer the chicken to a plate and set aside.",
    "Stir in the Gruyère cheese until melted and smooth.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste."
  ],
